    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.36.46"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">46</fw>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="caps">NEBRASKA WESLEYAN UNIVERSITY 
                        <lb/>
                    LINCOLN, NEBRASKA 
                        <lb/>
                        
                    OFFICE OF THE PRESIDENT</hi> 
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>May 23, 1972</dateline>
                    
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Dr. John <hi rend="caps">G.</hi> Neihardt</addrLine> 
                        <addrLine>5835 Vine Street</addrLine> 
                        <addrLine>Lincoln, Nebraska 68505</addrLine>
                    </address>
                    
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Thanks sincerely for your kindness in visiting with me yesterday. I greatly enjoyed this opportunity and am appreciative of your positive response to my suggestion that we try to establish some type of recognition for you on this campus.</p>
                
                <p>I have visited with the head librarian, Mrs. Lois Collings, and she will proceed immediately to determine the books under your authorship that we have currently on hand.</p>
                
                <p>Further, we shall endeavor to plan a specific event for early fall and will want you to come to the campus at that time. We are deeply appreciative of your expressed interest in this project.</p>
                
                <p>We are most anxious to have some of your materials, including an original manuscript for one of your books, to have on permanent display in the rare books section of our library.</p> 
                
                <p>Thanks for your assistance and best wishes always.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Very truly yours,</salute>
                    
                    <signed>Vance D. Rogers</signed>
                    <signed>Vance D. Rogers
                    President</signed>
                    
                    <note>VDR/ib</note>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
